snippet.title: Special Participation Video | gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
"Is this... New Eridu?"
"First time?"
"Well, not exactly. I've been here before, but it's been a while. What's new around here?"
"Heh, come on. Take a look at this~"

—Welcome to New Eridu!—
